| Phase | Feature | Impact | Effort |
|-------|---------|--------|--------|
| **Phase 1** (Now) | 🔒 **Domain + SSL** | Enables production use | Medium |
| **Phase 2** | 🔗 **Git Webhooks** (auto-deploy on push) | Matches the Vercel "magic" | Medium |
| **Phase 3** | 👁️ **Preview Deployments** (per-branch URLs) | Killer differentiator | High |
| **Phase 4** | 🌍 **Environment Variables UI** (proper editor, per-env) | Better DX | Low |
| **Phase 5** | 📊 **Monitoring Dashboard** (use existing `getPulse`, add charts) | Visualization of existing data | Medium |
| **Phase 6** | 💾 **Persistent Build Logs** (store, search, replay) | Enterprise-grade | Medium |
| **Phase 7** | 🗄️ **Database Management** (deploy Postgres/MySQL/Redis) | Dokploy parity | High |
| **Phase 8** | 📦 **One-Click Templates** | Onboarding accelerator | Low |

